UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Flames wreathe target within range. {@damage 8d6} fire damage on failed Dex save, half on success. Failed save burns target for duration—sheds bright light 30 ft, dim 60 ft. At turn end, target repeats save, taking {@damage 4d6} fire on fail. Flames can''t be extinguished by nonmagical means. Killed targets turn to ash.''' WHERE slug = 'immolation';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Summon devil (CR ≤6) in unoccupied space within range. Devil is unfriendly and rolls initiative. Command it via Charisma check contested by Wisdom (Insight)—advantage if you know true name. If command fails, devil immune to verbal commands but may still obey. Concentration ends at full duration, else devil acts freely for {@dice 3d6} min before vanishing. Requires magic circle binding.''' WHERE slug = 'infernal-calling';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Name/describe person, place, or object. You learn brief summary of significant lore about it. If not legendary, gain nothing. Info accurate but may use figurative language. More knowledge = more detailed info.''' WHERE slug = 'legend-lore';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'You become {@condition invisible}; illusory double appears where you stood (lasts duration). Invisibility ends if you attack or cast spell. Bonus action: move double 2× speed, make it gesture/speak. See/hear through double''s senses or your own (bonus action to switch). While using double''s senses, you''re {@condition blinded} and {@condition deafened}.''' WHERE slug = 'mislead';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Reshape target creature''s memories. Wisdom save; advantage if fighting. Failed save: target {@condition charmed}, {@condition incapacitated}, aware only you''re present. Affects event from last 24 hrs (≤10 min duration). Eliminate, perfect recall, alter, or create memory. Mind fills gaps. Broken concentration = no change. {@spell Remove Curse} or {@spell Greater Restoration} restores true memory.''' WHERE slug = 'modify-memory';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Bind celestial, elemental, fey, or fiend (within range whole casting). Charisma save. Failed save: bound to serve duration. Must follow instructions; hostile creatures twist words to own goals. If completes task, returns to report. If on different plane, returns to binding location. If summoned by other spell, that duration extended to match this.''' WHERE slug = 'planar-binding';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Touch dead creature (dead ≤10 days). If soul willing/at liberty, returns to life with 1 HP. Neutralizes poisons, cures nonmagical diseases. Doesn''t remove magical diseases/curses. Closes mortal wounds but doesn''t restore missing parts. −4 penalty all attacks, saves, checks (−1 per long rest). Can''t restore undead.''' WHERE slug = 'raise-dead';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Touch dead humanoid/corpse (dead ≤10 days). Forms new adult body, calls soul. {@dice d100} determines new form. Creature recalls former life, retains capabilities, exchanges old race for new one and racial traits.''' WHERE slug = 'reincarnate';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'See/hear particular creature on same plane. Target Wisdom save (modified by familiarity/connection). Creature aware = can voluntarily fail. Success: immune 24 hrs. Failure: invisible sensor within 10 ft target, moves with it. See/hear through sensor. Or target location seen before; sensor stays fixed.''' WHERE slug = 'scrying';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Change appearance of any number of creatures within range. Unwilling target Charisma save. Disguises physical appearance, clothing, armor, weapons. Make 1 ft shorter/taller, thin/fat/between. Can''t change body type. Physical inspection fails illusion (pass-through objects). Intelligence (Investigation) check vs. your DC reveals disguise.''' WHERE slug = 'seeming';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Call forth celestial spirit in angelic form within range. Uses {@creature Celestial Spirit} stat block. Choose Avenger or Defender. Ally to you and companions; shares initiative (acts after you). Obeys verbal commands or Dodges. Disappears at 0 HP or spell end.''' WHERE slug = 'summon-celestial';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Psychic energy explodes at point within range. {@damage 8d6} psychic damage in 20-ft-radius sphere; Intelligence save for half (Int 2 or lower unaffected). Failed save: muddled thoughts 1 minute—roll {@dice d6}, subtract from attacks, ability checks, Constitution saves to maintain concentration. Int save end of turn ends effect.''' WHERE slug = 'synaptic-static';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Move/manipulate creatures/objects by thought. Action each round: exert will on one creature/object within range. Creature (Huge or smaller): ability check vs. Strength save; win = move 30 ft (including up). Restrained in grip until end next turn. Object (≤1000 lbs): if unworn, auto-move 30 ft; if worn/carried, check vs. Strength save to pull away.''' WHERE slug = 'telekinesis';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Draw 10-ft-diameter circle inscribed with sigils linking to permanent circle on same plane. Portal opens, lasts until end next turn. Creature enters = appears 5 ft destination or nearest unoccupied space. Learn 2 sigil sequences initially, +1 per minute studied. Cast daily same location 1 year = permanent circle.''' WHERE slug = 'teleportation-circle';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Choose 40-ft cube stone/mud area. ROCK→MUD: nonmagical rock becomes mud, creatures sink (4 ft movement/ft mud), Strength save or {@condition restrained}. Ceiling mud falls—Dex save, {@damage 4d8} bludgeoning. MUD→ROCK: transforms to soft stone, Dex save shunts creature safe or {@condition restrained} (AC 15, 25 HP/inch, immune poison/psychic).''' WHERE slug = 'transmute-rock';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Enter living tree (≥your size), move inside to same kind within 500 ft. 5 ft movement to enter. Know location all same trees within 500 ft, move to one (5 ft movement). Appear 5 ft destination. Once per round. Must end turn outside tree.''' WHERE slug = 'tree-stride';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Invisible wall springs into existence within range. Horizontal, vertical, angled, free-floating, or resting. Form hemisphere/sphere (10-ft radius) or flat (ten 10-ft×10-ft panels, contiguous). 1/4 inch thick, lasts duration. Nothing passes through. Immune all damage, can''t be dispelled. {@spell Disintegrate} destroys instantly. Blocks ethereal travel.''' WHERE slug = 'wall-of-force';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Shimmering bright wall within range (≤60 ft long, 10 ft high, 5 ft thick). Blocks line of sight, creatures/objects pass. Bright light 120 ft, dim 120 ft beyond. Appearance: Constitution save or {@damage 4d8} radiant, {@condition blinded} 1 min (success = half, no blind). Blinded repeat save end turn. Creature ending turn in wall: {@damage 4d8} radiant. Action: launch beam (ranged spell attack) {@damage 4d8} radiant, reduce wall 10 ft.''' WHERE slug = 'wall-of-light';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Nonmagical stone wall springs into existence within range. 6 inches thick, ten 10-ft×10-ft panels (or 10×20 ft, 3 inch). Creatures pushed if cut; Dex save if surrounded. Shape freely (crenellations, battlements). Span >20 ft = halve panels. Object: AC 15, 30 HP/inch thick. Concentration whole duration = permanent, can''t dispel.''' WHERE slug = 'wall-of-stone';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Animate trees/rocks/grasses in 60-ft cube. Grass/undergrowth = difficult terrain for enemies. Trees: enemies within 10 ft make Dex save start turn or {@damage 4d6} slashing. Roots/vines: end turn, one creature makes Strength save or {@condition restrained} (action Strength check to break free). Rocks: bonus action launch at creature, ranged spell attack {@damage 3d8} bludgeoning, Strength save or {@condition prone}.''' WHERE slug = 'wrath-of-nature';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Create linked teleportation portals (duration). Two 10-ft-diameter rings: one ≤10 ft, one ≤500 ft. Creature/object enters one portal, exits other. Mist opaque, blocks vision. Visible one side only (your choice). Bonus action: rotate rings.''' WHERE slug = 'arcane-gate';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Vertical wall of whirling, razor-sharp magical blades within range (≤100 ft long, 20 ft high, 5 ft thick, or ringed ≤60 ft diameter). Provides three-quarters cover, difficult terrain. Creature enters/starts turn: Dex save or {@damage 6d10} slashing (half on success).''' WHERE slug = 'blade-barrier';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Up to six stone pillars burst from ground within range (≤5 ft diameter, ≤30 ft high). AC 5, 30 HP each. Reduced to 0 = rubble, difficult terrain 10-ft radius. Pillar under creature: Dex save or lift (creature can fail voluntarily). Pillar blocked by ceiling: {@damage 6d6} bludgeoning, creature {@condition restrained} (Strength/Dex check to break free).''' WHERE slug = 'bones-of-the-earth';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Summon fey (CR ≤6) or fey spirit/beast form (CR ≤6) within range. Fey friendly, rolls initiative, obeys verbal commands (alignment permitting). No commands = defends self. Broken concentration: lose control, becomes hostile, 1 hr before vanishing. DM has stat block.''' WHERE slug = 'conjure-fey';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Choose spell ≤5th level (1 action, can target you). Cast contingency + contingent spell (expend slots). Contingent doesn''t take effect until circumstance met. Takes effect immediately (even unwilling). Effect only on you. One contingency at time. Material component must stay on person.''' WHERE slug = 'contingency';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Cut yourself with jewel dagger, take {@damage 2d4} piercing. Drip blood on components, transform to faithful homunculus companion. Dies if you die. Long rest: spend ≤half Hit Dice, heal/increase homunculus HP (reduce your max to ≥1 HP). Can''t remove penalty until next long rest. One homunculus maximum. Fail if already have one.''' WHERE slug = 'create-homunculus';
UPDATE spells SET summary = 'Cast at night. ≤3 corpses (Medium/Small humanoids) within range become {@creature Ghouls} under control. Bonus action: mentally command within 120 ft (can command all, same order). Decide action/movement or general command. No command = self-defense only. 24 hr control; recast to maintain. DM has stat blocks.''' WHERE slug = 'create-undead';
